Quote: For the benefit of the inquirer, I may state that the pupurangi of the Maoris is Helix busber, and the largest land-snail in New Zealand. I have three specimens, and am willing to sell one or two at the price of GBP1 5s. each, having refused GBP1 1s. repeatedly.
